I"	<h1 id="gravity">Gravity</h1>
<p>A 3D web application to simulate three body problem. 
The goal of this project is to play with different web technologies.
This project was initially done for Semester Project - Virtualization 2 (WS2020 / 2021)</p>

<p><img src="https://github.com/shadlyd15/Gravity/blob/main/screeshots/1.png?raw=true" alt="Gravity" title="Gravity" /></p>

<h2 id="technologies-used">Technologies Used</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Docker Swarm</li>
  <li>Node.js for client API handling</li>
  <li>Python3 Flask for backend</li>
  <li>Three.js for 3D frontend</li>
  <li>Passport.js for JWT token authentication</li>
  <li>MongoDB</li>
</ul>

